PROTOWIZARD

aims to be a useful library for creating:
-games
-sound/music visualizations

uses the following libs:

GL3W for OpenGL defines and function grabbing 
https://github.com/skaslev/gl3w/

GLFW for window handling
https://github.com/elmindreda/glfw

GLM math lib
glm.g-truc.net/

SOIL for texture loading
http://lonesock.net/soil.html

BASS for sound playback and analysis (FFT)
http://www.un4seen.com/